# ─── Terraform ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# State files: can contain SECRETS (passwords, keys) in plain text.
# Never commit these. In real teams, state lives in a remote backend.
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*

# Provider plugins + cache: huge, machine-specific, re-downloaded by `terraform init`.
.terraform/

# Crash logs
crash.log
crash.*.log

# Variable files often hold secrets. Commit *.example versions instead.
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json

# NOTE: .terraform.lock.hcl is intentionally NOT ignored —
# it locks provider versions and SHOULD be committed.

# ─── Go ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Compiled binaries
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# Test binary / coverage output
*.test
*.out

# ─── Editor / OS ─────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
